Package model

Class User

java.lang.Object
model.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Authenticable, Contactable, Identification, PersonalDetails, RoleAssignable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Administrator, Doctor, Patient, Pharmacist
public class User extends Object implements Authenticable, Contactable, Identification, PersonalDetails, RoleAssignable
User Super class in the Hospital Management System (HMS). This class holds personal and contact details for a personnel, as well as their role in the system.

    • User

      public User(String UID, String fullName, String username, String email, String phoneNo, String passwordHash, LocalDateTime DoB, String gender, String role)
      Constructs a new User object with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      UID - the unique ID for the personnel
      fullName - the full name of the personnel
      username - the username of the personnel for system login
      email - the email address of the personnel
      phoneNo - the phone number of the personnel
      passwordHash - the hashed password for the personnel's account
      DoB - the date of birth of the personnel
      gender - the gender of the personnel
      role - the role or position of the personnel in the system
